name: opendatafiskeridirektoratet-testkommune.hub.arcgis.com
description: Data catalog for fisheries and aquaculture data from the Norwegian Directorate of Fisheries (Fiskeridirektoratet). Contains public and sensitive datasets such as registers for fishermen, vessels, licenses, environmental data, and aquaculture locations. Some sensitive data may be restricted, but much is available for download or via API.
